criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Aged between 18 and 65 years;
2. KPS score > 60 points and estimated survival time > 3 months; 
3. With confirmed hematological malignancies and to be treated with hematopoietic stem cell transplantation;
4. Without serious mental illness and serious heart, liver, kidney or pulmonary insufficiency, and other fatal diseases; 
5. Agreed to participate in this study, and signed the informed consent form.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Serious mental patient; 
2. Serious heart, liver, kidney or pulmonary insufficiency; 
3. In gestation period or suckling period; 
4. HIV infection or substance abuse.
